updated_cases.custom_steps:
1. Make sure the feature flag in feature_config.json is enable by default 
2. It can be disabled 
3. To disable it, modify the file /opt/ns/cfg/staged_config.json. 
Add a block Like: 
        {
            "name": "domain-fronting-exception",
            "data": {
              "enabled": true
            },
            "apply-globally": true
        }
# After Adding this, please remember to restart mtnsproxy service

